# Field & Stream Trip-ish

**Date**: 8/19/2020

**Learning Objectives**

After completing this tutorial you should

* be able to install the crowdwater app on your smart phone
* understand how to update virtual gauge, soil moisture, and temporary stream spots
* have signed up for four "asynchronous field trips"

